# FO4 inverter benchmark template
#
# Primary circuit-level validation target for OASIS-FinFET.
# Build a driver inverter, the DUT inverter, and a 4x load inverter.
# Measure delay at the DUT output while the DUT drives the 4x load input.
# Each proposed device must orient its drain-side composite spacer toward
# the switching output node of its inverter.
#
# Suggested topology:
# IN -> INV_driver -> INV_DUT -> INV_load_4x
#
# Extract:
# - tpHL and tpLH at the DUT output
# - FO4 delay = (tpHL + tpLH) / 2
# - output slew
# - average power
# - energy per transition
# - PDP or EDP
